# Admin Section Layout Consistency

For Admin tab work, use the same section/panel styling pattern used in existing Admin views.

- Use `detail-section` + `ui-panel-section` for top-level tab containers.
- Use `admin-people-card` (or existing `admin-proc-block` where already established) for major subsections.
- Use `detail-section-heading` with `h2` for tab title and `h3` for subsection titles.
- Do not introduce one-off wrapper classes for subsection cards when an existing shared class already fits.
- Reuse existing table/form wrappers (`ui-table-wrap`, `data-table`, `admin-people-form`) before adding new layout classes.
- If a new layout class is absolutely necessary, document why shared classes were insufficient in change notes.
